 a jacket or multiple sweaters. Do remember you will be hiking for at least one hour so your body will get warm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple.jpg\" alt=\"visit ijen tour sunrise view couple\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"visit ijen tour sunrise view couple\" class=\"wp-image-9591 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-couple-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/09\/23150818\/visit-ijen-tour-sunrise-view-cou